name: The Daily Good 14.3.22
description:
Today was a very productive beginning, ushering in the new paths ahead.

Just as this patch of daffodils growing in a ditch alongside the road have been busily blooming to usher in the spring that follows them.

I am grateful for the blooms I see now and very excited for the ones that are coming, both literally and metaphorically.

And I feel good about the accomplishments of the day.
